{"tid":1326460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"譚惠珠：示威者會慢慢淡化","createTime":"2019-07-17T08:32:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T08:42:09.000Z","uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"173a641d9b9289dbfb71189542d1a9a5aad78e54","tid":1326460,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T08:32:23.000Z","msg":"基本法委員會副主任譚惠珠出席回歸酒會後表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">政府清晰表示會聆聽民意，施政經充分諮詢，應做的事仍然會做，和市民的關係一定會更親切，被問到政府是否無法令示威者信服，她認為示威者會慢慢淡化</span>。<br />\n<br />\n至於政府如何回應示威者的五點訴求，譚惠珠認為，香港仍然需要這個團隊，相信一定會有改善，又批評要求撤回暴動定性是破壞法律，要求特赦是荒謬，認為訴求應該回答都已回答。"},{"pid":"1ad4a04b5d269544b3e722d5c94f37479d789cbf","tid":1326460,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T08:42:09.000Z","msg":"[緊急呼籲]［重要野好有用］今晚9點一齊上twitter將黑警濫權揚威國際，警告遊客不要來港旅遊，用經濟壓力逼使政府回應！！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1325723/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1325723/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全面攬炒<br />\n<br />\n9點一齊一野谷上trending <br />\n#Hongkongwarning #Fthepopo<br />\n<br />\nTwitter見！！！"}]}